overview: Starring exclusive contract super star, Jesse Jane alongside a delightful and sexy cast including Alicia Alighatti, Claire Robbins, Sandra Shine and Codi Milo! Directed by Celeste, Marvelous is an artistic masterpiece, a vision of decadence intertwined with pure eroticism and frantic lust. Jesse Jane is the recipient of numerous awards for her sexual prowess, including AVN's 2006 Best Girl/Girl Sex Scene. Watch her, as she leads a beautiful young cast into a foray of sexual bliss. With mood and music playing of the warm tones of flesh and fantasy, Celeste casts a warm and sexy light on the rich and privileged in this provocative springtime layout.
title: Jesse Jane: Marvelous
